{"tid":603458,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"招行去年盈利上升13%","createTime":"2018-03-23T18:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T22:06:46.000Z","uid":70274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e47778bb34f761d4fb866cd9944ba3d19edfdfc4","tid":603458,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:37:20.000Z","msg":"香港電台-財經<br />\n<br />\n招商銀行去年盈利701.5億元人民幣，按年上升13%，派息每股0.84元人民幣。<br />\n招行去年淨利息收入1448.52億元人民幣，增長7.62%，淨利息收益率2.43%，下跌0.07個百分點；非利息淨收入761.85億元，增長0.67%。<br />\n<br />\n期內不良貸款率1.61%，按年下降0.26個百分點，不良貸款餘額下降37.28億元，實現「雙降」。不良貸款撥備覆蓋率262.11%，按年提高82.09個百分點。<br />\n高級法下招行資本充足率15.48%；一級資本充足率13.02%，分别按年上升2.15及1.48個百分點。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/招行去年盈利上升13-120237551.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E6%8B%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8713-120237551.html&d=cNPXH2SfTmEmQcKn40XQjzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=f3cd12c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/招行去年盈利上升13-120237551.html</a>"},{"pid":"b2e96e194854cf6ec80987312ab89eeada07745f","tid":603458,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:06:46.000Z","msg":"搵多左 好消息出貨 要跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}